name: Experiment Or Die #98
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. When I moved to Georgia in 2004 the bugs and spiders all doubled in size and quantity compared to upstate NY. Most of them were harmless but they sure were intimidating. I never imagined I'd be living in Georgia but was following a dream of mine so I found a way to make it work and went. You have to make the necessary change in your life to make those dreams a reality. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
